text: Struggled to finish this because I had no appetite, but the Hainanese pork chop was actually pretty decent. Skip the curry chicken though.

Ordered signature tonkatsu here. It was good üëç

Reasonable price and quick serving.

The rest of the dish was looking delicious as well. Nice presentation of the dishes.

Food is generally quite ok.
I ordered the spicy ramen.
The pork was very tasty.
However, the ramen was a bit disappointing.

Hans food never fails. Staff are friendly, helpful and warmth. Curry chicken is delicious. The new special Pineapple rice with satay is yummy. I like the home made ice lemon tea .. sedap!  Everything is good. Oh yah, not to mention the pies. Always enjoy eating at Hans so far even in other branches.
Very nice cafe at Bird Paradise. Han's food has always been consistently good. Surprise to find ramen in menu. Quite tasty. However, the coffee, tea & toast are disappointing.
